PDVSA

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Petróleos de Venezuela)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






This article needs to be updated. Please update this article to reflect recent events or newly available information. (February 2016)



Petróleos de Venezuela S.A.









