	(1)


	          


	Our refineries
	sourced 78%, 81% and 81% of our total crude oil requirements from crude oil
	produced by us in 2003, 2002 and 2001, respectively.




	(2)


	          


	Sourced by us
	(including supplies from entities that are not subject to our control).




